'''''Boba Fett and X-Wing: The Mandalorian Candidate''''' was a crossover story-arc or miniseries for the ''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron]]'' comics, proposed by [[Andy Mangels]]. In it, [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] would have teamed up with [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] to discover an enemy agent with Rogue Squadron, and who his employer was. Mangels discussed it with [[Dark Horse Comics]] and very briefly with [[Michael A. Stackpole]], but it was never published.

